Tahj Mowry https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tahj_Mowry 0 Tahj Dayton Mowry (; born May 17, 1986) is an American actor and singer. Mowry is the younger brother of identical twins Tia Mowry and Tamera Mowry. He is known for his show Smart Guy as the main character TJ on The WB, though the show gained later notoriety on the Disney Channel. Mowry was later cast as a ten-year-old super genius Wade Load on Kim Possible as a nod to this role. He is also known for his role on Full House playing Michelle's best friend, Teddy. Tahj also played Tucker Dobbs on Freeform's hit comedy show Baby Daddy. Tahj_Dayton_Mowry ( ; born May_17_,_1986 ) is an_American_actor_and_singer .
